  "text": "I'm going to take a wild guess and say it's the Meta work. Am I right, or is the lawn calling your name?"
}

{
  "text": "Chalk up another one! You're on a roll, Eric. What's next on the hit list?"
}

{
  "text": "You crushed it in about an hour. Efficiency for the win!"
